=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"944cbb1388985bc3bb7ac560e236f59c3f132120","tid":1800093,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7888efd0ee31a4f80b7b476ca2c56f4475f28a8b","tid":1800093,"uid":308618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3320d74ef1432987a537ba0643680c5e6776d880","tid":1800093,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9039937c5c6c9ca162ed0774a50eeed30fa2ff4","tid":1800093,"uid":323360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"學業？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:06:09.000Z","msg":"其中一部份係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"仲有咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"我人在異地 仲努力適應緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}